<!-- Node: "Half-Life 2 code theft arrest" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Half-Life 2 code theft arrest</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Thursday, June 10, 2004 - 18:37</small><br /><br />
<a href = "http://www.gamespot.com">Gamespot</a> got an article about Half-Life 2 source code theft arrest. Valve CEO Gabe Newell announced that source code theft were arrested thanks to the gaming community, which tracked/led to the arrests, within a few days of the announcement of the break-in. Read full article <a href = "http://www.gamespot.com/news/2004/06/10/news_6100381.html">here</a>.
